Now NAME is an adult, living life to it's full potential in his parents' basement.
You could say he's done it all. But he would disagree. NAME's whole life was there to prepare him for his final journey. A journey into...
It's an ancient conspiracy, older than civilisation itself. The criminal underworld of the sewers is the most powerful organisation on the planet. People think it's crazy, but NAME knows better than that.
In pursuit of ultimate power, to become king of the underworld, NAME abandons his family home and delves deep into the dark below.
